{"tid":1262501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癲之地獄鬼國 - China 開幼兒園作性奴隸養成 網友大爆料 中國孤兒院提供客人性侵幼童","createTime":"2019-06-27T17:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:16:51.000Z","uid":141060,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0707026b8d71e406952217b917b095622984466","tid":1262501,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-4974746-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-4974746-1-1.html&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=99779a8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-4974746-1-1.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/27/rci1S6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F27%2Frci1S6.jpg&h=752db1ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/27/B9sxLv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F27%2FB9sxLv.jpg&h=d00a11c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/27/sjTyfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F27%2FsjTyfe.jpg&h=e48e620e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaacsJG.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaacsJG.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=beceb95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全部爆料內容 all content：<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-4974746-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-4974746-1-1.html&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=99779a8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-4974746-1-1.html</a></span></strong><br />\n中國大陸曾爆發過幼稚園虐童事件，當時事件涉及施打不明針筒、餵食不明藥物及性侵，雖然引起國際關注，但最終卻被中共當局壓下，結果今（27）日又爆出有中國孤兒院提供客人性侵幼童的消息，且這次還有數張照片同時流出佐證，引起中國網友震驚。<br />\n中國貴州驚傳爆發性侵幼童事件，有孤兒院的孩童疑似被院方利用，提供性服務給對幼童會感到興奮的20～40歲民眾，為了讓幼童快速長大，還會依照客人要求施打黃體酮（黃體素、孕酮）荷爾蒙讓女童身材「快速長大」，並讓女童看A片洗腦，甚至讓其他女童圍觀性侵現場。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，同時被爆出來還有數張聊天截圖，其中竟然有數張女童遭玩弄的照片，還有人用詼諧的態度分享去過後看到的情景，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一切的一切都讓網友看得毛骨悚然，相關搜尋甚至一度登上微博熱搜，不過僅管有這麼多證據擺在眼前，中共當局卻仍稱是造謠，隨後將相關訊息全部封鎖、刪除。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e513c12b56fb4a92e360b6177c855daf3580900","tid":1262501,"uid":54181,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:15:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6582c3be2331c19a2e00d0886161e51c26145313","tid":1262501,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4be39ea9e577323a7a5747f6de8d67290a1a33","tid":1262501,"uid":73419,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"支拿有野係真既咩 FACT CHECK 未先"},{"pid":"0642787f9e9674466de6daefe530231da692627d","tid":1262501,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37df29ddcbd9128a35fd56d59f9074fbab732946","tid":1262501,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"link有面有埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7c27b101b73311414b8fa0e20bada415845653","tid":1262501,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵人fact check下係邊到傳出黎先<br 